Class QuantisedLocalFeature<L extends Location>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.feature.local.quantised.QuantisedLocalFeature<L>
  • Type Parameters:
    L - the type of Location
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    FeatureVectorProvider<IntFV>, LocalFeature<L,IntFV>, LocalFeatureVectorProvider<L,IntFV>, LocationProvider<L>, Readable, ReadableASCII, ReadableBinary, ReadWriteable, Writeable, WriteableASCII, WriteableBinary
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    QuantisedAffineSimulationKeypoint, QuantisedKeypoint

    public class QuantisedLocalFeature<L extends Location>
extends Object
implements LocalFeature<L,IntFV>
    A QuantisedLocalFeature is a local feature with a single integer feature-vector.
